Achievements.Name: Chapter 1 - Welcome to Woolington
Achievements.Description: You completed the first chapter! Thanks to Libretta you managed to escape from the Conroyalists.

Achievements.Name: Chapter 2 - Prison Escape
Achievements.Description: You completed the second chapter! You knocked out Emil and escaped from the prison.

Achievements.Name: Chapter 3 - The Center of the World
Achievements.Description: You completed the third chapter! You complied with all the traveling regulations..

Achievements.Name: Chapter 4 - Reunion in Old Aspia
Achievements.Description: You completed the fourth chapter! You repaired a Basylian and blasted open the gate to the mountains

Achievements.Name: Chapter 5 - The Secret of the Foggy Valley
Achievements.Description: You completed the fifth chapter! Now you know the secret of the last wind monk!

Achievements.Name: Chapter 6 - Wind of Change
Achievements.Description: You ended the Conroyalist's reign of terror. Now all of Aposia knows the truth about Emilâ€¦

Achievements.Name: Feeding the drill rats
Achievements.Description: You showed your fondness of animals by feeding some sawdust to the drill rats.

Achievements.Name: If at first you don't succeed
Achievements.Description: Failures won't stop you from trying again - good for you! But now try something else please.

Achievements.Name: Knock-Knock Master
Achievements.Description: Hello, anybody home? Uncle Oboe's crazy game of Knock-Knock was no match for your brilliant mind.

Achievements.Name: Mr. Wise-Guy
Achievements.Description: You didnâ€™t use the help system! Congratulations, you can consider yourself an Adventure expert!

Achievements.Name: Public Enemy No. 1
Achievements.Description: You disobeyed the system by removing the travel poster in Asposia Central. Congratulations!

Achievements.Name: Return to sender
Achievements.Description: Bravo! You're a reliable person! Screwdriver, syringe, stapler - you bring back what you borrow.

Achievements.Name: Who cable cares?
Achievements.Description: Who cares about the cable car model of some weird shopkeeper? You certainly don't!

Achievements.Name: Back in bag
Achievements.Description: You filled the sneezing powder from its bag into the balloon. And back again. Wow.

Achievements.Name: Bingo!
Achievements.Description: You restored the Bingo Pony's confidence to face life again!

Achievements.Name: Boom!
Achievements.Description: You sabotaged Mama Dola's ritual with a chili. Bravo! What a fine explosion, indeed!

Achievements.Name: Casual-Gamer
Achievements.Description: Until now, youâ€™ve been using the help system quite often. Youâ€™re a casual-gamer for sure!

Achievements.Name: Green is not a creative color
Achievements.Description: You tried giving the peas to Libretta, so she could use them for painting..

Achievements.Name: Kick it like Peacham
Achievements.Description: You flushed a peach straight in front of the key guard's feet, kicking it right back into your cell.

Achievements.Name: Monolith
Achievements.Description: You solved the Monolith puzzle! Let's hope all that flute music didn't cause permanent damage to you

Achievements.Name: Negative thinking doesn't pay off
Achievements.Description: You fixed the ticket machine, and thanks to the negative cashflow-wiring you even have to pay for it

Achievements.Name: One doused root lizard
Achievements.Description: Three times you doused the root lizard with water. No wonder he's mad at you!

Achievements.Name: Raft ride
Achievements.Description: You sent a small raft sailing across the swamp. How nice. But now back to saving the world!

Achievements.Name: Story Wizard
Achievements.Description: You got Uncle Oboe's adventure story right at the first time! But where's the fun in that?
